'''''Batattis''''' was a modified [[CorelliSpace]] [[Gymsnor-3 light freighter/Legends|Gymsnor-3 light freighter]] owned by the [[Ho'Din/Legends|Ho'Din]] terrorist [[Ort Hoogra-D'En]]. He had the ship hidden in his base on [[Pallaxides]]. He planned to use it to escape the planet in the event of an attack. His escape would involve launching two decoy [[Freighter/Legends|freighters]] before he escaped.

